Second Department,

April, 1942.

(April 1, 1942.) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Ralph Giffone, Appellant, v. The Warden and Agent of City Prison, Respondent.

On argument, order dismissing writ of habeas corpus reversed on the facts, writ sustained, bail fixed at the sum of $25,000, and relator remanded to the custody of the warden and agent of the city prison, Brooklyn. Lazansky, P. J., Carswell, Adol, Taylor, and Close, JJ., concur.
